or Heinrich Bruening that the cabinet would not shrink from an open dic tatorship if the new reichstag failed to give it a majority vote The Bruening cabinet is strong er than many seem to think said the Korrespondenz Kraus news agency of the Catholic or Centre party of which Bruening is leader Democratic principles are all right and the peoples decision should be respected but if r the peo ple elect a reichstag which means the countrys ruin the government must take matters into its own hands JAPAN IMPOVERISHED CHURCH GIFTS FALL Contributions at Toklos Coney Island Drop to 125 Daily By"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-22T13:12:30.961Z", "group": ["ndnp/in", "indiana-state-library-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82015313/1930-09-26/ed-1/?sp=21", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:in:batch_in_goldman_ver01:data:sn82015313:0038334928A:1930092601:0447/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=275&w=197", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:in:batch_in_goldman_ver01:data:sn82015313:0038334928A:1930092601:0447/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=550&w=395", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:in:batch_in_goldman_ver01:data:sn82015313:0038334928A:1930092601:0447/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1100&w=791", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/in/batch_in_goldman_ver01/data/sn82015313/0038334928A/1930092601/0447.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 21, "language": ["english"], "location": ["indianapolis", "marion county", "indiana", "marion", "united states"], "location_city": ["indianapolis"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["marion"], "location_state": ["indiana"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["3", "4", "8", "0", "2", "a", "1", "9", "sn82015313", "0000000021"], "number_edition": ["1